            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>I fratelli <persName key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name
                                ref="Robertus">Roberto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge">giudice del sacro palazzo</rs> e
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Ildebrando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs> del <persName>fu <name ref="Petrus"
                                key="#Notary">Pietro</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs>, <persName><name ref="Berta"
                            >Berta</name></persName>, moglie del suddetto Roberto e figlia del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Serectus">Seretto</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Adalasia">Adalascia</name></persName>, moglie
                        del suddetto Ildebrando e figlia del <persName>fu <name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildebrando</name></persName>, avendo ricevuto <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">meritum annulum unum aureo</rs> pro
                        180 soldi dal <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName> pro persona di
                            <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Leo">Leone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abate</rs> del <rs key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di
                            <orgName key="#Houses #Monasteries #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/71">San Ponziano</orgName> di <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Lucca</placeName>, e di <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Giovanni</name></persName>, rector de <rs key="#Hospitals"
                            >hospitale</rs> suprascripti Sancti Pontiani, con il consenso dei
                        rispettivi mariti promettono di non contestare medietate di una <rs
                            key="#Houses">casa</rs> et re massaricia posta in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3305">Stabbiano ubi dicitur a la
                            Leccia</placeName>, tenuta da <persName><name ref="Stephanus"
                                >Stefano</name></persName> massarium, quas vobis odie per <rs
                            key="#Venditio">cartula</rs> scripta ex manibus del <rs
                            key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Cuneradus"
                            >Corrado</name></persName> ex comparatione obvenit a nos ipsis. Se non
                        rispetteranno i suddetti impegni, promettono con i loro eredi di versare
                        all’abate, al rector e ai loro successori la pena di 20 libbre d’argento.
                        Chiedono al notaio imperiale Corrado la stesura della cartula. Actum Luca.
                            <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rusticus">Rustico</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Paulus">Paolo</name></persName> di <persName
                            key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rodilando</name></persName> di <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Antonius/Sapiebonus">Antonio</name> detto
                            Sapiebono</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
